      "amount": "1/4 cup",
      "notes": "chopped"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and ginger and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the amazake and cook, stirring constantly, for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the spices, salt, and butter and stir until the butter has melted.",
    "Add the couscous and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a mini cocotte and serve hot.",
    "Garnish with parsley and serve immediately."
  ],
